title: CRED REA Fish Team Belt Transect Survey at Saipan, Marianas Archipelago, 2005
name: cred-rea-fish-team-belt-transect-survey-at-saipan-marianas-archipelago-2005
notes: Belt transects along 3 consecutively-placed, 25m transect lines were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments conducted at 8 sites at Saipan in the Marianas Archipelago (MA) during 3 September - 1 October 2005 in the NOAA Oscar Elton Sette (OES 0511) Reef Assessment and Monitoring Program (RAMP) Cruise. Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
